§ Labyrinth.of.Apocalypse · systems · fps_pipeline
≡ T11-W13-FPS-PIPELINE · W13-1 FPS-render-pipeline + perf-rebuild
≡ canonical-companion : compiler-rs/crates/loa-host/src/fps_pipeline.rs
≡ STATUS : ◐ shipped-stage-0 · iterates each FPS-wave
≡ PRIME-DIRECTIVE : ¬ harm/control/manipulation/surveillance ; consent-OS

§I role
  W! LoA-expanding-to-action-FPS-looter-shooter ⇒ frame-budget-discipline = sovereignty
  ¬ ALL : fps_pipeline ⊆ catalog-only-Rust ⊑ no-runtime-deps
  ALL  : 7 disjoint render-architecture surfaces wire to single FpsPipeline
    1. RingBuffer<N>        · triple-buffered frames-in-flight (N=3 default)
    2. PassDescriptor       · multi-pass declaration (depth-prepass · opaque · transparent · post)
    3. CmdBufferPool        · pre-allocated cmd-buffers · zero-per-frame-Vec-grow
    4. CullingPlan          · GPU-driven cull-compute-shader plan (frustum+occlusion)
    5. VrsTier              · variable-rate-shading tier-table (foveated · 1×1 → 2×2 → 4×4)
    6. PresentMode          · mailbox (low-latency · ¬vsync-block · stretch 144Hz)
    7. FrameMetrics         · per-frame tag · cmdbuf_recycled · cull_active · vrs_pixel_ratio

§I focus-areas (Apocky-mandate)

  W! 1.frame-budget-discipline
    ✓ ≤8.33ms (120Hz) · stretch ≤6.94ms (144Hz)
    ✓ FRAME_BUDGET_144HZ_MS = 6.944 added to polish_audit
    ✓ sub-frame input-latency target = ≤2ms input-to-display

  W! 2.multi-pass-architecture
    Pass-0 depth-prepass        · opaque-only · z-only · feeds occlusion-cull
    Pass-1 GPU-cull-compute     · async-compute · culls Pass-2/3 instance-list
    Pass-2 opaque                · MSAA·HDR · culled-instances only
    Pass-3 transparent           · alpha-blend · back-to-front sorted
    Pass-4 shadow-maps           · async-compute · 4-cascade-CSM
    Pass-5 SSEffects             · async-compute · SSAO/SSR/Bloom
    Pass-6 tonemap (existing)    · ACES RRT+ODT
    Pass-7 CFER (existing)       · alpha-blend volumetric ω-field
    Pass-8 UI overlay (existing) · final composite

  W! 3.zero-allocation-hot-path
    W! ¬ Vec::push in render_frame
    W! ¬ Box::new in render_frame
    W! ¬ String::from in render_frame
    ✓ pre-alloc CmdBufferPool · capacity = ring-depth × pass-count
    ✓ pre-alloc UniformStaging · ring-N × bytes-per-frame
    ✓ pre-alloc InstanceBuffer · 65536-instance cap · grow-only-on-overflow

  W! 4.triple-buffering
    ✓ RingBuffer<3> · 3-frames-in-flight default
    ✓ waitable-fence per slot · device.poll(Wait(fence_id))
    ✓ slot.lifecycle = Free → Recording → Submitted → Presented → Free
    ✓ never-block-CPU on GPU @ frame-N+2 boundary

  W! 5.GPU-driven-culling
    ✓ frustum-cull compute-shader · per-instance · workgroup-64
    ✓ occlusion-cull via Hi-Z from depth-prepass
    ✓ indirect-draw-args buffer · culled-instance-IDs only
    ✓ catalog-side : CullingPlan + cull-test-bench (CPU mirror for parity)

  W! 6.async-compute
    ✓ shadow-maps + SSAO + bloom run on async-compute queue
    ✓ scheduled to overlap Pass-2 opaque-fragment work
    ✓ catalog-side : DispatchPlan + queue-priority enum

  W! 7.variable-rate-shading
    VrsTier ⊗
      Tier1 = 1×1 (full-rate)        · center-region · radius ≤ 25% screen
      Tier2 = 2×1 / 1×2              · mid-ring     · 25% → 60%
      Tier3 = 2×2                    · outer-ring   · 60% → 90%
      Tier4 = 4×4                    · periphery    · 90% → 100%
    foveated-mode : eye-tracker-aware (stretch ; default = static-radial)
    pixel-ratio bench : ~0.42 saved-shading at default-radial

  W! 8.frame-pacing
    ✓ PresentMode = Mailbox (default-stretch · ¬tearing · ¬block)
    ✓ fallback PresentMode = Fifo (vsync-block · safety-default)
    ✓ user-toggle via setting low-latency ⊗ {true → Mailbox, false → Fifo}

§I attestations
  zero-alloc       : pipeline-construct-zero-alloc-test ✓
  no-leak          : 1000-frame-no-leak-test ✓
  cmd-buffer       : recycle-test ✓ (slot reuse-counter sat-tracking)
  ring-depth       : 3-slots strictly-honored · no-4th-recording ever
  frame-budget     : on-CPU-only path verifies-budget at default-1080p

§I integration-points (siblings)
  W13-2 weapons        : uses our InstanceBuffer for projectile-batched-draw
  W13-3 network        : reads FrameMetrics.frame_id for snapshot-tagging
  W13-4 camera         : uses PresentMode.matches_vsync? for prediction model
  W13-5 ADS-recoil     : reads VrsTier per-frame for foveation-jitter
  W13-6 movement       : tagged by FrameMetrics.frame_id for replay
  W13-7 HUD            : draws after Pass-8 · uses our final-composite handle
  W13-8 loot           : InstanceBuffer + culled-draw-list
  W13-9 battle-pass    : spec-only · ¬render-touch
  W13-10 gacha         : spec-only · ¬render-touch
  W13-11 input         : reads PresentMode for input-latency-budget
  W13-12 perf-enforcer : reads PerfBudget · attestation-gate

§I PRIME-DIRECTIVE attestation
  ¬ surveillance : VRS foveated-mode is OPT-IN ; never reads eye-tracking by default
  ¬ engagement-bait : pacing optimizes for player-perceived-latency only
  ¬ harm : higher-fps reduces motion-sickness · accessibility-aligned
  Apocky-greenlit per W13-1 mission : action-FPS-grade frame-budget = sovereignty

